text: Groussbus-Wal is a commune in northwestern Luxembourg. It is part of the canton of Redange. It was created on 1 September 2023 from the former communes of Grosbous and Wahl. As of 2023, 1,134 people live here. Category:2023 establishments in Europe Category:21st-century establishments in Luxembourg Category:Communes of Redange
title: Groussbus-Wal
